						<div class="postbody">Values written to $4011 are not signed. $40 is center,[1] $00 is bottom, and $7F is top.
<br />
<br /><span style="font-size: 84%; line-height: normal">[1] Almost. The DAC is in fact slightly nonlinear, though not nearly as much as on the Game Gear. </span></div>

